Package: libdebian-package-make-perl
Architecture: all
Depends: ${perl:Depends}, dpkg-dev, libwww-perl, libfile-copy-recursive-perl
Description:  Perl modules for automatically generating Debian packages
 Debian::Package::Make::* is a set of modules that simplify the
 process of writing make-*-package programs (scripts that
 automatically generate Debian packages).
 .
 This is useful for source distributions where contents change too
 frequently for manual building or where peculiar licenses prohibit
 redistribution via public package repositories.
Tag: implemented-in::perl